HEADWORD: Cartogram
<hw>Car"to*gram</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>cartogramme</ets>.]</ety> <def>A map showing geographically, by
shades or curves, statistics of various kinds; a statistical
map.</def>⟦br⟧
